    {
      "id": 22,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "End-to-End Latency (ms, EMA)",
      "description": "Measured at the sink (last filter, webvis). total_time = full wall-clock frame journey from source to sink \u2014 NOT the sum of the per-filter process() times on the left. It is larger because it also includes ZMQ transmission time between filters, queue wait times, and scheduling overhead. One series per pipeline (each pipeline has one sink). For fan-in pipelines (P3 diamond, P4 diamond-same-class), total_time reflects the critical path (slowest branch) \u2014 that is the Bug 2 fix. avg_time = average per-stage process() time. std_time = jitter between stages.",
